snippet.title: Castaway 2 Speedrun Former WR (2:21:02)
snippet.description:
My speedrun of Castaway 2! I was able to do it in 2:21:02. Not all that good, but it's a start!

Edit: It's official! I have the world record for the fastest time to beat Castaway 2!

Edit 2: After 4 years, my run was finally beat. Props to AWalkingPineapple for beating it! His run can be found on the speedrun.com leaderboards here: https://www.speedrun.com/httparmorgames.complay11261castaway-2
